        "ev-fa7a4e500330888d"
      ],
      "text": "Flow-specific gates must not duplicate permission policy with checks such as direct cameraGranted, locationGranted, nearbyGranted, notificationGranted, hasMissingImmediatePermission, or hasPartialImmediateGrant branches."
    },
    {
      "evidence_ids": [
        "ev-37246da5f65a00b3"
      ],
      "text": "It must reject work that was created from a permission state that would not pass flow entry."
    },
    {
      "evidence_ids": [
        "ev-37246da5f65a00b3"
      ],
      "text": "Do not copy browser-specific fallback logic into sync."
